title: All My Alter Egos Are Tycoons
description: All My Alter Egos Are Tycoons Manhwa My Kingpin Dopplegangers , My clone is becoming a giants , 내 분신이 거물이 되어간다, Sovereign of the Infinite Clones Novel Name: My Alter Ego’s Path to Greatness Synopsis : A young man, Han Sunghyun, loses his family in an indiscriminate attack by superhumans. While living a reclusive life due to the trauma of the incident, one day, he awakens the ability to control avatars in his place! “What?! I can send avatars to hunt in dangerous otherworlds while I stay safely at home, just focusing on strengthening my powers?!” As his avatars grow rapidly, crossing dimensions, races, and professions, Han Sunghyun begins to hunt down the superhumans who abuse their powers!
alternative_titles: My clone is becoming a giants
My Alter Ego’s Path to Greatness
